### 请求 /cps/adzone/create 接口 => 成功（淘宝默认推广位）
POST {{baseUrl}}/cps/adzone/create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}

{
  "platformCode": "taobao",
  "adzoneId": "mm_taobao_default_pid",
  "adzoneName": "淘宝默认推广位",
  "adzoneType": "general",
  "relationId": null,
  "relationType": null,
  "isDefault": 1,
  "status": 1
}

### 请求 /cps/adzone/create 接口 => 成功（会员专属推广位）
POST {{baseUrl}}/cps/adzone/create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}

{
  "platformCode": "taobao",
  "adzoneId": "mm_taobao_member_1001",
  "adzoneName": "会员1001专属推广位",
  "adzoneType": "member",
  "relationType": "member",
  "relationId": 1001,
  "isDefault": 0,
  "status": 1
}

### 请求 /cps/adzone/update 接口 => 成功
PUT {{baseUrl}}/cps/adzone/update
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}

{
  "id": 1,
  "adzoneName": "淘宝默认推广位（更新）",
  "isDefault": 1,
  "status": 1
}

### 请求 /cps/adzone/delete 接口 => 成功
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/cps/adzone/delete?id=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}

### 请求 /cps/adzone/get 接口 => 成功
GET {{baseUrl}}/cps/adzone/get?id=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}

### 请求 /cps/adzone/page 接口 => 成功
GET {{baseUrl}}/cps/adzone/page?pageNo=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}

### 请求 /cps/adzone/page 接口 => 按平台+类型筛选
GET {{baseUrl}}/cps/adzone/page?pageNo=1&pageSize=10&platformCode=taobao&adzoneType=general
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}

### 请求 /cps/adzone/list-by-platform 接口 => 成功（淘宝推广位列表）
GET {{baseUrl}}/cps/adzone/list-by-platform?platformCode=taobao
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}

